Spellcheck with:
    $ hunspell -d en_US file # the default dictionary is en_US

If no dictionary can be found (Can't open affix or dictionary files for
dictionaty names "en_US"), then download dictionary and affix files, en_US.dic
and en_US.aff, and put it in any directory listed in hunspell -D (for example,
~/.openoffice.org/3/user/workbook).
